channel.title: Ideas for a stork like server?
channel.description:
[center]Im [b]ALMOST[/b] done with a [b]stork like[/b] server. no not GOOGLE or YAHOO.[/center]
Anyways since [size=12pt][b]alot[/b][/size] of this community wants a pking server i wanted to run some shit by you and see what you think.
[center]I think there should be a [size=18pt][b]NO MONEY BASED ECONOMY[/b][/size] in this server.[/center]
Basically what i mean is train and then pick up shit you never have to worry about selling or buying shit.
[ul][li]I will make all pking supplies easy to obtain and basically nothing is a hand me out. --i.e. a man will drop all basic runes by 25 so when you kill one you can get either an air fire water etc etc and have 25 of it.[/li]
[li]Dragons will drop rune items not insanely hard but you need to work hard so 1-25 will drop something rune based not just full rune but pointless rune shit also like arrows.[/li]
[li]I will make it so only edge have objects to focus only activity inside edge and the wilderness only.[/li][/ul]
[size=24pt][b]Only thing that is free is FOOD[/b][/size]
[center][b]In total i mean you have to obtain shit by training your points.[/b][/center] [center][size=18pt] [b]NO SHOPS NO COINS.[/b][/size] [/center] [center][b]Lemme know wtf you think and if i should add anything or wtfux. [/b][/center]

item.dc:creator: @Officer_Barbrady Officer Barbrady
item.description:
@Officer_Barbrady wrote:

[quote=“mapu, post:75, topic:365690”][quote author=Officer Barbrady link=topic=461892.msg3382588#msg3382588 date=1288162916]

What is my real alias?

You are asking us what your alias is. You’re displaying excellent spikes of intelligence for somebody who calls others morons.

We do however have your information.

Good one, if that made any sense. Anyone with half a brain could see that I’m clearly doubting that you know my past alias’s and I’m just taunting you. It’s just a shame how stupid you’ve become.

You have my *old* IP, which I didn’t even bother to hide - Congratulations. However it has already been changed hours ago. Now you have nothing.

Tell that moron “nobot” to chose harder passwords this time. LOL.[/quote]
I would have had you DDoS’d when I had the chance if I actually cared what your current ip was.

I use ip’s simply to trace people’s alias’s. Unfortunately for you I haven’t even bothered looking. The most I did was post a topic on my forum asking if anybody knew your last alias and they came back with some information about you.

Your previous alias is as insignificant as your current one. I was just curious but it seems this has escalated as you’ve tried to make it sound like you’re some awesome hacker who can use a proxy and create another moparscape account.

WOOP-DI-FUCKIN-DOO

Curiosity doesn’t get the best of me, but it seems a marginal amount of attention given to you goes straight to your head.[/quote]

If you actually cared? The way I see it, you had to have gotten my IP from here. Since you have xEnt on your team, I have to assume it was him, and then of course searched your site for any matching IPs. You also added that IP to your htaccess. To me that seems like you cared

DDoSed me LOL, you probably tried and stopped when you realized you were hitting an outdated IP.

You have nothing on me, else you would have threw it in my face a long time ago. I just don’t understand why you and Old Rsc Player are so full of it.

I would love to know how you came to figure they were “insignificant” when you can’t even figure out who I am.

Watch out Mapew he a hack3r!!!!

Keep believing your a programmer; No one else does.
